OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780315873
OL,3,COliver Glasner says Palace got 'what
OL,4,Cthey deserved' after conference league
OL,5,Cwin
OL,7,FDeparting boss Oliver Glasner felt
OL,8,FCrystal Palace finally got "what they
OL,9,Fdeserved" after beating Rayo Vallecano
OL,10,F1-0 in Leipzig to win the Conference
OL,11,FLeague and book a place in the Europa
OL,12,FLeague next season.
OL,14,FIt was the competition Palace
OL,15,Finitially thought they had qualified
OL,16,Ffor after the Austrian, who managed
OL,17,Fhis last Eagles match at the Red Bull
OL,18,FArena, led them to their first major
OL,19,Fsilverware when they lifted the FA Cup
OL,20,Fin 2025, then the Community Shield.
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
