OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780315873
OL,3,COliver Glasner says Palace got 'what
OL,4,Cthey deserved' after conference league
OL,5,Cwin
OL,7,FThen came disappointment in the form
OL,8,Fof a multi-club ownership conflict and
OL,9,Fa denied appeal to the Court of
OL,10,FArbitration for Sport, ultimately
OL,11,Fdemoting Palace to UEFA's third-tier
OL,12,Fcontinental competition.
OL,14,FGlasner, speaking after Jean-Philippe
OL,15,FMateta's second-half goal proved the
OL,16,Fwinner in the 1-0 win, said: "You need
OL,17,Fgreat, talented football players, of
OL,18,Fcourse but you need great characters.
OL,26,@xD@^OU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780315873
OL,3,COliver Glasner says Palace got 'what
OL,4,Cthey deserved' after conference league
OL,5,Cwin
OL,7,F"So they deserve all the credit, and
OL,8,Fat the end it's now with a one-year
OL,9,Fdelay at Crystal Palace. The players,
OL,10,Fthe club, the supporters all get what
OL,11,Fthey deserved last year after winning
OL,12,Fthe FA Cup, and a spot in the Europa
OL,13,FLeague."
OL,15,FGlasner in January announced he would
OL,16,Fdepart Palace at the end of the
OL,17,Fseason, and replied with a firm "no"
OL,18,Fwhen asked if the victory had inspired
OL,19,Fany doubts about his decision to leave.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@HO]yD@aOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
