PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780315873
OL,3,COliver Glasner says Palace got 'what
OL,4,Cthey deserved' after conference league
OL,5,Cwin
OL,7,FThe reality of the end of his tenure
OL,8,Fonly set in, said the 51-year-old, who
OL,9,Falso led Eintracht Frankfurt to Europa
OL,10,FLeague glory in 2022, at the final
OL,11,Fwhistle.
OL,13,FGlasner slid face-first through a
OL,14,Ftunnel of his red-and-blue striped
OL,15,Fplayers before they ascended the
OL,16,Fvictors' podium to collect their
OL,17,Fmedals.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780315873
OL,3,COliver Glasner says Palace got 'what
OL,4,Cthey deserved' after conference league
OL,5,Cwin
OL,7,FSome sections of those in attendance
OL,8,Fbooed UEFA officials, including
OL,9,Fpresident Aleksander Ceferin, in the
OL,10,Fpost-match ceremony.
OL,12,FBut the feeling in Leipzig was
OL,13,Foverwhelmingly euphoric for a fanbase
OL,14,Fwho have watched their club bounce
OL,15,Fback from the brink of administration
OL,16,Fto, in the span of Glasner's less-than
OL,17,Ftwo-and-a-half-year tenure, win three
OL,18,Ftrophies and a major European title.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
