PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780315873
OL,3,COliver Glasner says Palace got 'what
OL,4,Cthey deserved' after conference league
OL,5,Cwin
OL,7,FMateta's goal was inspired by player-
OL,8,Fof-the-match Adam Wharton, who will
OL,9,Fonce again leave some scratching their
OL,10,Fheads as to why he was omitted from
OL,11,FEngland boss Thomas Tuchel's World Cup
OL,12,Fsquad.
OL,14,FIt was his initial shot from range
OL,15,Fthat stung the palms of Rayo keeper
OL,16,FAugusto Batalla and fell into the path
OL,17,Fof the World Cup-bound France
OL,18,Finternational, who poked it home and
OL,19,Fset Palace on their way to the Europa
OL,20,FLeague.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
