FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780315873
OL,3,COliver Glasner says Palace got 'what
OL,4,Cthey deserved' after conference league
OL,5,Cwin
OL,7,FWharton, who was a fitness concern
OL,8,Fbefore this contest, later admitted
OL,9,Fthat there was "a lot of doubt" about
OL,10,Fhis ability to start, after having his
OL,11,F"foot in an icebox for the last couple
OL,12,Fof days, just trying to get the
OL,13,Fswelling down."
OL,15,F"I couldn't really shoot fully," he
OL,16,Fconfessed. "It wasn't very
OL,17,Fcomfortable, but I'm not going to miss
OL,18,Fa final for a little swollen ankle."
